Windows 7 ... at least it's better than Vista.

System requirements:
 - VBE2-compatible BIOS
 - 4 MiB RAM
 - Floppy-station
 - Monitor capable of viewing 24bpp in 640x480 mode.
Or:
 - A virtual machine giving you the above mentioned resources.

To compile you need:
 - fasm: flatassembler.net

See attached Makefile for build instructions.

XKCD-reference: http://xkcd.com/528/
